    SchemaMappingReader.read(org.apache.jena.graph.Graph mappingDescription)
    Parses the given RDF description of a schema mapping into a Map in which every global term of the schema mapping is a key that is associated with a set of all TermMappings that have the global term as their getGlobalTerm().
